      <description>&lt;p&gt;As a doctoral fellow, I am researching new paradigms at the intersection of XRAI and AEC Industry (Buildings and Spaces) at the AI:Xpertise Lab, as part of &lt;a href=https://www.en.aix.aau.dk/&gt;AI:X Labs&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=https://vap.aau.dk/&gt;VAP Lab&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=https://www.aicentre.dk/&gt;Pioneer Centre for AI (P1)&lt;/a&gt;, at Aalborg University (AAU). I am working on XRAI4AEC, under the supervision of &lt;a href=https://vbn.aau.dk/en/persons/anmo&gt;Prof. Andreas Møgelmose&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=https://vbn.aau.dk/en/persons/elm&gt;Prof. Kasper Elmholdt&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=https://vbn.aau.dk/en/persons/tbm&gt;Prof. Thomas Moeslund&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
